 x#22 B-SHIFT-R x#02 is 00008
00010 B-LEFT  x#05   is 00320
00010 B-RIGHT x#02   is 00002
30067 B-SHIFT-LC 4   is 22327
30067 B-SHIFT-RC 4   is 14167
